      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-exp-zac-200.
       exe-exp-zac-800.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Close files                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Chiusura del file in output                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "CL"                 to   g-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mcvout"
                                         using g                      .
